abstract: In the past year, the site has invested $20,000 in search engine optimization. "We were not pleased with the results," the owner said. "It was not worth the cost."

lead_paragraph: Dr. Debra Jaliman has run a dermatology practice in Manhattan for the past 25 years. Ten years ago, she created a Web site to promote both her practice and her line of skin-care products.

headline.main: Does This Service Provider's Web Site Make You Want the Service?
